  <p>This introduction is based on your expertise in {{advisorIndustries}} and your service coverage in {{advisorGeographies}}.</p>
  
  <p>Best regards,<br>
  The Advisor-Chooser Platform Team</p>
  
  <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
